# 🔁 Logout Flow (Saga Optional)

### Simple logout:

```js
dispatch({ type: LOGOUT })
```

### Saga-based logout (for API/session cleanup):

```js
function* logoutSaga() {
  yield call(apiLogout)
  yield put({ type: LOGOUT })
}
```

